Q: Maybe the index.html in template folder is needed only when django is used?
A: It is needed even when django is not used!

2. In package.json, this line is important. As it opens the server because of it.
Otherwise it cannot be run.
"scripts": {
    "dev": "webpack-dev-server --mode development --open --watch index.js --output ./static/frontend/main.js"

But before this in terminal , run npm i -D webpack-dev-server